#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reading an Existing <filename>/etc/fstab</filename> Is No Longer Supported"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: ay_12_migrate_15.xml:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &productname; 15 the ability to read an existing <filename>/etc/fstab</"
"filename> from a previous installation when trying to determine the "
"partitioning layout, is no longer supported."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: ay_12_migrate_15.xml:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting for Aligning Partitions Has Been Dropped"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: ay_12_migrate_15.xml:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As cylinders have become obsolete, the <tag class=\"element"
"\">partition_alignment</tag> &gt; tag makes no sense and it is no longer "
"available. &ay; will always try to align partitions in an optimal way."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
